reviewText:
Maybe I'm old fashioned or am not sufficiently with it to investigate more closely, but I was expecting videos of season 5. It is, after all
called volume 5. This was from the very early TV show and not what I wanted. You can sometimes find what episodes are in the
videos, although it means a lot of searching around.
Had to get they all.  Watched as a kid

I grew up with the TV series "Fury", great memories!

Thank you so much for a great transaction!
